item.title: CVE-2023-1805|2024-08-02T06:05:26.097Z -- unknown -- product%20catalog%20feed%20by%20pixelyoursite
item.description: The Product Catalog Feed by PixelYourSite WordPress plugin before 2.1.1 does not sanitise and escape the page parameter before outputting it back in an attribute, leading to a Reflected Cross-Site Scripting which could be used against high privilege users such as admin

item.title: CVE-2023-1804|2024-08-02T06:05:25.524Z -- unknown -- product%20catalog%20feed%20by%20pixelyoursite
item.description: The Product Catalog Feed by PixelYourSite WordPress plugin before 2.1.1 does not sanitise and escape the edit parameter before outputting it back in an attribute, leading to a Reflected Cross-Site Scripting which could be used against high privilege users such as administrators.
